27:24.394 --> 27:25.812
You don't have any more fortune.

27:25.979 --> 27:28.315
I'll write one for you.
In the very near future,

27:28.481 --> 27:30.400
you give the fuckin'
leprechaun his coin back,

27:30.567 --> 27:31.985
lie down, and rot.

27:32.610 --> 27:33.945
Wanna try your luck?

27:35.196 --> 27:37.198
All my luck is yours,
dead wife.

27:37.365 --> 27:40.910
Don't need to read about it.
Just break the fuckin' machine.

27:44.080 --> 27:45.999
So, over the centuries,

27:46.166 --> 27:50.003
people in other countries
felt called to places of power.

27:50.170 --> 27:52.088
They knew there was
an energy there,

27:52.255 --> 27:55.717
a focus point, a channel,
a window to the Immanent.

27:55.884 --> 27:58.928
And they built churches,
cathedrals,

27:59.095 --> 28:01.973
or they'd, they'd erect
a stone circle.

28:02.140 --> 28:03.808
Well, you get the idea.

28:03.975 --> 28:05.894
But there's churches
all through the States.

28:06.061 --> 28:07.979
No, in the good old USA,

28:08.146 --> 28:10.273
people still heed the call
of the transcendent void,

28:10.440 --> 28:12.150
but they respond to it

28:12.317 --> 28:14.069
by building a model
out of beer bottles

28:14.235 --> 28:15.737
of somewhere
they've never visited,

28:15.904 --> 28:17.906
or by erecting
a giant bat house

28:18.073 --> 28:19.574
in some part of the country

28:19.741 --> 28:21.826
that bats have traditionally
declined to visit.

28:22.410 --> 28:24.537
Or they sell T-shirts
and hotdogs.

28:24.704 --> 28:26.164
Roadside attractions!

28:26.331 --> 28:28.875
Where they buy that hotdog
and they buy that T-shirt.

28:29.042 --> 28:32.003
And then they wander around
feeling satisfied on a level

28:32.170 --> 28:34.130
that they cannot truly describe,

28:34.297 --> 28:37.926
and profoundly dissatisfied
on a level beneath that.

28:38.093 --> 28:40.428
You know, you have got some
pretty whacked-out theories.

28:40.595 --> 28:44.099
Nothing theoretical about it,
you should know that by now.

28:44.432 --> 28:47.477
Time... to ride.

29:16.589 --> 29:18.550
Feel the power, Shadow.

29:26.641 --> 29:31.104
Like a prayer wheel going round
and round, accumulating power.

29:31.604 --> 29:33.523
Gazed upon by the faithful.

29:59.841 --> 30:01.718
If you follow the signs,

30:01.885 --> 30:04.095
