32:39.083 --> 32:40.793
We're just backstage.

32:41.836 --> 32:43.546
Waiting in the wings.

32:44.297 --> 32:47.300
Inside Wednesday's memories.

32:48.926 --> 32:50.845
All right, so, you... what...?

32:51.012 --> 32:53.056
You're saying we're in his head?

32:53.222 --> 32:54.766
More or less.

33:00.813 --> 33:03.858
