first came to America,

35:17.116 --> 35:19.243
they brought us with you.

35:20.495 --> 35:25.249
Me, Loki, Thor, Nancy...

35:26.167 --> 35:29.504
the Lion-God, all of you.

35:30.838 --> 35:33.174
