and took root.

35:33.716 --> 35:37.553
But gradually, they abandoned us
for a better deal.

35:38.221 --> 35:40.515
A new life in a new land.

35:41.974 --> 35:45.978
Our true believers passed away,
or stopped believing.

35:46.562 --> 35:48.648
Left us to fend
for ourselves,

35:48.815 --> 35:52.235
to get by
on what little smidgens

35:52.401 --> 35:55.154
of belief or worship
we could find.

35:55.321 --> 35:58.157
And that's what we've done.
We've gotten by.

35:58.741 --> 36:01.994
We live in cracks
at the edges of society.

36:02.161 --> 36:04.914
Old, forgotten Gods

36:05.081 --> 36:07.333
in a land without Gods.

36:07.500 --> 36:10.044
But there are New Gods
growing in America.

36:10.211 --> 36:12.463
