I see no battlefields.

37:03.472 --> 37:05.266
I hear no war cries.

37:05.641 --> 37:08.644
Then you are not
looking hard enough, Mama-ji.

37:09.145 --> 37:10.605
Odin's right.

37:12.565 --> 37:15.401
These New Gods
have more followers,

37:15.568 --> 37:17.153
more attention,

37:17.320 --> 37:19.155
more power

37:19.322 --> 37:20.823
